Note on dictionary content licensing:

The MIT license above applies to the BUILD CODE (build.py and supporting
scripts) authored by Murat Uysal. The compiled dictionary content
(english-turkish-dictionary.mobi) is derived from two upstream sources and
carries their licenses:

  * English Wiktionary translations (via kaikki.org Wiktextract):
    CC BY-SA 4.0 and GFDL.

  * FreeDict eng-tur v0.3 (originally gtksozluk2 by Mehmet Ali Vardar):
    GNU GPL v2.0 or later.

Because GPL is the more restrictive of the two and CC BY-SA 4.0 is one-way
compatible with GPLv3, the combined .mobi artifact is effectively distributed
under the GPL v2.0 or later. End users may redistribute the .mobi file under
those terms; the build code itself remains MIT.
